# neo-ui-preservation

When this rule applies, read and follow:

`.cursor/skills/neo-ui-preservation/SKILL.md`

## Quick guardrails

- Keep **`Robot2D`** as the live centerpiece; do **not** enable **`Robot3D`** on this branch.
- No wholesale shell redesign, generic card layouts, or panel repositioning without explicit approval.
- Prefer the smallest change; do not introduce a new global layout framework for HUD work.

## Completion

End with: **protected UI preserved** — yes/no, plus short notes (what stayed fixed, any intentional visual delta).
